<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A plain <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="block">block</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">2.06</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.59</measure> × depth not measurable).</p>
