<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>
Both texts <rs type="execution" key="scalpro">inscribed</rs> on the face, which is cracked, i. to the left, ii. to the right. The block is complete above, though chipped; i. must therefore have begun on an upper block.</p>
</div>

